Miami Private Events
Miami Private Events
Ray's wants to host your next event! Wedding after parties, actual weddings, photoshoots, film shoots, corporate gatherings, comedy shows, you name it, we can do it.
Conveniently located in Miami Beach on 27th Street and Indian Creek Drive (along Mid Beach), we are within walking distance of:
LIV Nightclub
Faena
Edition
Cadillac
AC Hotel
as well as a short ride away from:
Soho House
Fontainebleau Hotel
Email
info@raysbarnyc.com
for a quote.
First Floor
Standing capacity 100
Seated dinner capacity 60
Second Floor
Standing capacity 100
Seated dinner capacity 50
Full Buyout
Standing Capacity 225
Includes first and second floor, two bars, and outdoor patio
